===Etymology===
Derived in the [[w:Heian period|Heian period]] from writing the [[man'yōgana]] kanji [[末]] in the [[cursive]] [[sōsho]] style. [[変体仮名|Variants]] include those derived from [[万]], [[萬]], [[満]], [[馬]], [[間]], [[摩]], [[漫]], [[真]] and [[麻]].

